+++++++++
Cron Job
+++++++++

mta @ r2d2-v

2 19 * * 6  cd /data/mta4/www/DAILY/mta_src/Exc; /data/mta4/www/DAILY/mta_src/Scripts/hrma_focus.py >> $HOME/Logs/hrma_focus.cron 

